course_description: This course is a continuation of CS 170. Emphasis is on the use and implementation of data structures, fundamental algorithms with introductory algorithm analysis, and object oriented design and programming with Java.
prerequisites: CS 170 or CS_OX 170 or equivalent transfer credit as prerequisite.
